snippet.title: Hypersomnia multiplayer gameplay (4 versus 4)
snippet.description:
Forgive the green flickering light on characters - it was a rendering bug.
This is a 2019 footage way before headshots and penetration were added.

Download and play online: https://hypersomnia.xyz
Join our Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/YC49E4G

You can build the game yourself - it's free and open source!
https://github.com/TeamHypersomnia/Hy...
